wiki.summary: “PUFFIN ON ZOOTIEZ” is the fifth track on Future’s ninth studio album "I NEVER LIKED YOU". This song’s snippet, which was previously named “Hermès Astronaut” by fans (they misheard “Hermès ashtray” for “Hermès astronaut”), went viral after Future had posted it to his Instagram story on November 1, 2021. Zootiez is also a brand that Future has collaborated with to help promote the album. There was a listening party for the album on the Zootiez discord server Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “PUFFIN ON ZOOTIEZ” is the fifth track on Future’s ninth studio album "I NEVER LIKED YOU". This song’s snippet, which was previously named “Hermès Astronaut” by fans (they misheard “Hermès ashtray” for “Hermès astronaut”), went viral after Future had posted it to his Instagram story on November 1, 2021. Zootiez is also a brand that Future has collaborated with to help promote the album. There was a listening party for the album on the Zootiez discord server, where fans were also able to hear a couple of songs from the album a few hours before its eventual release.
